{
  "stem": "4967.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I-- I went back to work [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as a messenger boy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I decided [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that it's a good idea to-- to-- to go away from this camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Seeing new people coming in, and the old ones, they'll liquidate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's not a proposition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They don't get-- they don't let people to get-- to get acclimatized.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If you stay in one place too long, they know you're getting too clever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So anyway, took me some doings to work with my old man, let him rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I was still running as a Laufer, working in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day came the order in the morning that the camp must be cleaned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Spotlessly cleaned because there's going to be an-- an inspection from a general from Zurich, Switzerland, to come to see the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And a delegation from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And a German High Command is coming to check the camp. 1944-45 was this already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we cleaned the camp this day and the next day and the day after.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The people went to work, and we worked in the camp. 11 o'clock, the whistle goes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Everybody must go to the appellplatz, where they counted people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Where they speak to the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They counted people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the all inmates who worked in the camp had to assemble in this place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't come from Geneva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't come from Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't come from nowhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came High Command Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
